text.section:
On or before the 28th day of each month, the Division shall provide to the superintendent or other officer in charge of police in the municipal corporation or county from which the inmate was committed the following information about each inmate whose sentence expires the following month:
the inmate's name;
the date when the inmate's sentence commenced;
the county from which the inmate was committed;
the crime for which the inmate was committed; and
the exact date when the inmate will be discharged.
